79 NEW (47 + 32) Bundle 6.0.4 lower-body cluster milestone 4-bundle clean sweep cumulative 165 NEW + Memory edit"},{"date":"2026-05-13k","note":"APPEND chat-current chat ACASĂ post Strategic 'fese' canonical cluster + Session Sequence Ordering V1 LANDED 4 atomic commits clean Bugatti single-concern — **Co-CTO autonomy MAXIMUM trust delegation cross-chat 5th consecutive directive pattern** (2026-05-13g + 13h + 13i + 13j + 13k = 5× consecutive trigger pattern verbatim). Daniel verbatim 13k *\"nu am ce decizie sa iau... make it happen ca e core function. Si la fese la fel. Daca ai ceva sa ma intrebi please do, scurt si simplu cat sa inteleg (si sa nu fie cto decision side)\"* — MAJOR Co-CTO autonomy total trust delegation MAXIMUM directive verbatim limit întrebări la UX/scope visible NU tactical decisions side. 2 NEW ADR LOCK V1 raw layer Co-CTO autonomous (ADR_ANATOMICAL_CLASSIFICATION_V1 + ADR_SESSION_SEQUENCE_ORDERING_V1) = strategic LOCK V1 trust delegation MAXIMUM continuat preserved invariant. Handover trigger directive *\"handover\"* — 5 consecutive trigger directive pattern verbatim courier zero pentru handover §F3.8. Co-CTO autonomy LOCK V1 PERMANENT preserved invariant unchanged."}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/concepts/autonomy-paradigm-v1.md"},
